{
  "stem": "7744.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "In fact, when some of these people ran back to Russia, when the Germans entered Lwow, they came in the middle of the night and begged us to go back with them to Russia.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But of course, my father felt-- and particularly my mother-- that under German, German rule, it would never be bad.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because she truly believed that after all, a nation such as, such well, such well-educated nation, a nation of such stature, could not be any worse than some of the people who were so backward as in Russia.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So it was very interesting.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In '41, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] quite-- I can't tell you timewise, because it's sort of a little difficult--",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--for me to, to put the clock on, on things and the time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I think that was in the first week or two they gathered-- the Germans, the Gestapo gathered-- all the intelligentsia-- and particularly, not only, not only Jewish intelligentsia, but Polish intelligentsia, too.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They came.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They took my father away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we've never seen him again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, people are asking me, don't you know if he died?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Don't you know what happened to him?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Did they send him someplace?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the presumption was, since we have never heard from him again-- and I'm sure that my mother at that time must have made an awful lot of inquiries, because she had a lot of connections-- that they must have killed these people.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Where and how, I couldn't tell you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, no, no, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At this point, I'm nine years old.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm nine years old.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm nine years old, and I come from a family where I wasn't exactly a child that was exposed to a lot of life reality.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
